I  N  F  O  R  M  A  T  I  O  N

Rogue Legacy is a genealogical rogue-"LITE" where anyone can be a hero.

Each time you die, your child will succeed you. Every child is unique.

One child might be colorblind, another might have tourettes-- they could

even be a dwarf. That's OK, because no one is perfect, and you don't have

to be perfect to win this game.
